		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_ABBEY_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Abbey is the Mudruvese unique building, replacing the Temple. It grants +2 [ICON_PEACE] Faith as well as +1 [ICON_HAPPINESS_1] Happiness and +1 [ICON_FOOD] Food. The Abbey provides an additional +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith if the city was founded next to a river, plus a further +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith for each mountain within the city's borders. Units garrisoned in the city also gain an additional +5 HP per turn. After Flight is researched, the Abbey grants +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism as well.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_ABBEY_HELP">
			<Text>Mitruhmoer's unique building replacing the Temple, the Abbey rewards settling next to rivers with mountains in the vicinity with [ICON_PEACE] Faith. It also heals units faster and slightly increases [ICON_HAPPINESS_1] Happiness and [ICON_FOOD] Food. Provides +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism after Flight is researched.</Text>
